{"tid":213241,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇-我唔係屈機男-點解要成日上網扮有錢佬 ?","createTime":"2017-04-23T04:12:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T05:58:44.000Z","uid":103921,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f8d8df88193b099c092e177a3c14b1ee8259d178","tid":213241,"uid":103921,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T04:12:28.000Z","msg":"被人踢爆扮有錢佬, 敗走高登後. 諗住去連登再扮有錢佬, 點知...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實屈機男現實是咪矮柒毒? <br />\n<br />\n03:06AM 仲見佢連登開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d772199064b655229130fe32754688adf65fbe4","tid":213241,"uid":53068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T04:14:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>被人踢爆扮有錢佬, 敗走高登後. 諗住去連登再扮有錢佬, 點知...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實屈機男現實是咪矮柒毒? <br />\n<br />\n03:06AM 仲見佢連登開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇舊post睇下"},{"pid":"4becb96634119374f2347a82357d7d6c14fd688a","tid":213241,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T04:14:24.000Z","msg":"我接受呀<br />\n<br />\n你敢唔敢接受米蛇挑戰?<br />\n<br />\n你避米蛇就返屋企吔屎啦, 搵我做擋箭牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b1a77817f9b2e362d589342ae0e5ae946afb5e","tid":213241,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T04:16:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>被人踢爆扮有錢佬, 敗走高登後. 諗住去連登再扮有錢佬, 點知...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實屈機男現實是咪矮柒毒? <br />\n<br />\n03:06AM 仲見佢連登開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇舊post睇下</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>有冇簡介<br />\n係咪上次吹到好勁一開波就捐錢點知比人反cup個2個</blockquote><br />\n劇情回顧:<br />\n屈機男在高登常以有錢佬姿態教化高登仔做人道理<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R0i1Q28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR0i1Q28.jpg&h=c884d968&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屈機男常自稱有幾個物業, 但又睇淡樓市<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W1Bp683.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW1Bp683.jpg&h=14ab5e98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/69n6byc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F69n6byc.jpg&h=508c64cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屈機男以高高在上姿態雄霸財經台, 而且有一眾信眾追隨.<br />\n然而, 直至會員 米已成炊出現, 他質疑屈機男之有錢言論, 多次挑戰其財經台權威.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3u76373.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3u76373.jpg&h=476a844a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是大發明家屈機男發明了解決糾紛方法...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ly869i3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLy869i3.jpg&h=be0daf5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/009PHw5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F009PHw5.jpg&h=dcad78a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屈機男及其信眾一直強勢, 欺侮米已成炊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eKrCVnV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeKrCVnV.jpg&h=33bd4d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgX65WO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgX65WO.jpg&h=c0ddb46e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FVg6J3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFVg6J3M.jpg&h=f50358a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都係直接飛到結局.... 屈機男捐唔起錢認輸, 而其信眾亦鳥獸散或深潛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V6d859G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV6d859G.jpg&h=bb060f2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pw1pgUy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPw1pgUy.jpg&h=7c7dbc8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q8NL1v6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq8NL1v6.png&h=401336d2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9e7202f79c5c34fc08585c93df42681f96ed3078","tid":213241,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T04:16:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>走數狗屈機男 信佢果個真係要驗腦</blockquote><br />\n弱智<br />\n<br />\n岩岩先ko左件阿域<br />\n<br />\n另外，我走左邊條數？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/009PHw5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F009PHw5.jpg&h=dcad78a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明話輸左永久退出高登, 但又定期上水留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Opwr82D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOpwr82D.jpg&h=d8cfee9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n走數狗屈機男 信佢果個真係要驗腦</blockquote><br />\n自己言而無信，偏偏寫文成日廢up教人做人要上進反省<br />\n垃圾就是垃圾<br />\n笑話永遠係笑話</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e337b09bbb60ed898674ff8124a499882eb64f93","tid":213241,"uid":72399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T04:19:48.000Z","msg":"呢條7頭除左識同人鬥捐錢 /屌人唔讀書仲識咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f09b0bfa7ebfedc825464bb3c6cc79817a4ae9","tid":213241,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:32:05.000Z","msg":"咁有錢，不如貼下幾多張差餉或者交幾多稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"222608d03a353f178670bd651495d5f147a88653","tid":213241,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:35:14.000Z","msg":"保安狗"},{"pid":"b21d158616f3a2ea6259333fcbae51a5e9c235a2","tid":213241,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:35:58.000Z","msg